# Project Layout

```
Kingdom/
├── main.py                          # Entry point: python main.py
├── config.py                        # All tuning constants, costs, sizes, colors
├── requirements.txt                 # pygame, openai, anthropic, google-generativeai, httpx, python-dotenv
├── CHANGELOG.md                     # Version history (update on release only)
│
├── game/
│   ├── engine.py                    # Main game loop, input, coordination
│   ├── world.py                     # Tile map, fog of war
│   ├── entities/                    # Hero, Enemy, Building, Peasant, TaxCollector, Guard, Lair
│   ├── systems/                     # Combat, Economy, Bounty, Spawner, Lair, Buffs, Pathfinding
│   ├── ui/                          # HUD, panels, menus, widgets, theme
│   ├── graphics/                    # Sprite generators, animation, VFX, font cache
│   ├── audio/                       # AudioSystem + event contract
│   └── sim/                         # Timebase, determinism, contracts, guardrails
│
├── ai/
│   ├── basic_ai.py                  # Hero AI decision loop (no-LLM and LLM paths)
│   └── providers/                   # LLM provider adapters (openai, claude, gemini, grok, mock)
│
├── assets/
│   ├── sprites/                     # Pixel art: heroes/, enemies/, buildings/, workers/
│   ├── audio/sfx/                   # Sound effects (.wav/.ogg)
│   ├── audio/ambient/               # Ambient loops (.ogg)
│   └── ui/                          # UI skin assets (9-slice, icons)
│
├── tools/
│   ├── qa_smoke.py                  # QA gate: python tools/qa_smoke.py --quick
│   ├── validate_assets.py           # Asset gate: python tools/validate_assets.py --report
│   ├── determinism_guard.py         # Static determinism checker
│   ├── observe_sync.py              # Headless behavior observer
│   ├── capture_screenshots.py       # Deterministic screenshot runner
│   └── assets_manifest.json         # Expected assets list
│
├── docs/
│   └── screenshots/                 # Baseline + manual screenshots
│
└── .cursor/
    ├── rules/                       # THIS FOLDER — SOPs for all agents
    └── plans/
        ├── studio-agent-cards_*.plan.md   # Full agent card definitions
        ├── agent_logs/                     # Per-agent JSON logs (1 file per agent)
        └── *.plan.md                       # Sprint plan files
```

## Key constants location

All game tuning lives in `config.py`: costs, sizes, speeds, HP values, spawn rates. Check there before hardcoding numbers.

## How to run the game

```
python main.py                    # Default (mock AI, borderless window)
python main.py --no-llm           # No AI decisions (basic patrol only)
python main.py --provider mock    # Mock LLM provider (deterministic)
python main.py --provider openai  # Real LLM (needs .env with API key)
```
